# Test the AOP Example API - Auto-Registration with Controllers
# Demonstrates [RequireAdmin] at class level, method level, and on services

### Test 1: Public endpoint (should work without admin header)
GET http://localhost:5054/api/user/public

###

### Test 2: Admin endpoint WITHOUT admin header (should fail with 401)
GET http://localhost:5054/api/user/all

###

### Test 3: Admin endpoint WITH admin header (should succeed)
GET http://localhost:5054/api/user/all
X-User-Role: Admin

###

